{"tid":1436887,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★零售舖位驚現劈價潮　蝕四成放盤無人吼","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T11:29:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ba785fdf05f2357674739e4653ca04f0e98fc6","tid":1436887,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"近月社會不穩，加上中美貿易戰持續，香港零售氣氛轉差，灣仔、堅尼地城及旺角區都有舖位業主看淡後市，以蝕讓價求售物業。當中灣仔駱克道有街舖以低於購入價約400萬元或逾四成放盤。有市場人士認為，市場舖位價格普遍要劈價兩成才較吸引。<br />\n<br />\n綜合市場資訊，近月舖位市場陸續出現多數宗蝕讓放盤個案，當中蝕幅較大的為上述駱克道單號地舖，面積約95方呎，早前曾以750萬元放售，隨後劈至650萬元，由於依然未獲承接，最新再減至498萬元。該舖位現由小型地產公司以每月約8,500元承租，租約期至2021年初。據了解，該舖位2012年購入價為890萬元，即最新意向價，較買入時大幅低約44%或392萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190809/bkn-20190809070003203-0809_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190809%2Fbkn-20190809070003203-0809_00842_001.html&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq388up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=2910ac03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190809/bkn-20190809070003203-0809_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0ec34acc3eb809682e23cfd30d8bb56b7d16b4ac","tid":1436887,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57842824a73cdcc46f1773ff3921a7e6f9270f9b","tid":1436887,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067120736c7db446b77d82039841792725454d0e","tid":1436887,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"[經濟戰] 中共林鄭最怕香港信貸評級下跌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/